### Hadith 2:275

*Narrated Ibn 'Umar:*

I remember ten Rakat of Nawafil from the Prophet, two Rakat before the
Zuhr prayer and two after it; two Rakat after Maghrib prayer in his
house, and two Rakat after 'Isha' prayer in his

house, and two Rakat before the Fajr prayer and at that time nobody
would enter the house of the Prophet Hafsa told me that the Prophet used
to offer two Rakat after the call maker had made the Adhan and the day
had dawned.

